{"id":"2023-japan-06","collection":"2023-japan","date":"2023 February 14 - 15","title":"Hakuba - Happo-one + Rest Day","content":"First day on the snow was at Happo-one, about 20 minutes walk from my accommodation.\n\nUnfortunately the weather wasn't the best, but I still had a decent enough first day on the snow, finding my legs again after quite a few years...\n\nThe next day I was happy to wander about town since the weather was a little intermittent again. The town is quite pretty with all the snow around. While I was walking around I stumbled across a really nice looking restaurant with an insanely well-priced katsudon set, so I had to give it a go - it was fantastic, complete with very authentic seating on tatami and rowdy locals having their lunch around me!\n\nAfter lunch I decided I would go to a hot spring that had great reviews over the train line and on the edge of town. This was a bit of a walk, but the reward of onsen overlooking the valley and mountains more than made up for it. Definitely enjoy onsen in the snow!","images":[{"src":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/d/1TcnlKNFa7uaHlRr-Qng2Js1DzEDxHHHk?authuser=0","collageSrc":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/d/1PYrs-jdSAW7qq3pY1GOhC_G7mxhkssf9?authuser=0","navSrc":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/d/1QLkXbVlgbxQv1b6SjJi1BMjeqQf2OrXV?authuser=0"},{"src":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/d/1UGV1qHYw5jci0OBOjdl2kbbbKkVv3p2h?authuser=0","collageSrc":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/d/1il3dkkE07Mg-Me8yjGyObVaKuxztKo1l?authuser=0","navSrc":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/d/1AgoRQaFeox9qaHaUghc3L_dkswbsSt4q?authuser=0"},{"src":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/d/1UQDgs-nWJzeaAqXaCV2DGIN5D8qcz-dE?authuser=0","collageSrc":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/d/1rYdP3jUEMwI9h0BzXE_T_zewaUKg45ON?authuser=0","navSrc":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/d/13WVTNJ3WmS29pCE6vPxAeRbBn-xnQxi1?authuser=0"},{"src":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/d/1AdqgcNjrdWKjkz-rtkiE-ChY4s9F_u1d?authuser=0","collageSrc":"htt